quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,AL M
  2,2,"That The Book no doubt/suspicion in it, (it is) guidance to the fearing and obeying"
  2,3,Those who believe with the unseen/hidden and they keep up/call for the prayers and from what We provided for them they spend
  2,4,"And those who believe with what was descended to you, and what was descended from before you, and with the end (other life) they are sure/certain"
  2,5,Those are on a guidance from their Lord and those are the successful/winners
  2,6,"That those who disbelieved, (it is) equal/alike on (to) them, had you warned them , or you did not warn them, (notice) they do not believe"
  2,7,God sealed/stamped on their hearts/minds and on their hearing and on their eye sights/understanding a cover and for them (is) a great torture